utils module¶

class utils.utils¶

Bases: object

load_model_compressed(filename)¶
Description

Load model weights & configurations into compressed format. parameter filename: file which loads into the model. :type filename: string. :returns: loaded_nn.

save_model_compressed(model, filename)¶
Description

Save model weights & configurations into compressed format. :parameter model: object from class. :type model: object. parameter filename: file which saves into the model. :type filename: string. :returns: None.
